description:
Good news everyone! We're back (again), kind of. We're hoping to run a lightning talks night before the end of the year but thought it would be ideal to have a social first to get some ideas percolating. Plus at Kongs, we have a chance to play some retro arcade games.

While the majority of COVID issues seem to be behind us if you're feeling unwell please stay at home - there will be more events!

We'll cover your 1st drink but you'll probably want some food either before or at Kongs (https://kongsbars.co.uk/).

If you have any questions or concerns please do get in touch with one of the organisers via meetup or ask in the SWmobile slack. Look forward to seeing you!

P.s If you have ideas of talks or types of events you'd like to see and you cannot make this event please reply.
title: 🍻 November Social 🍻
